TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {13824=This trunk strut is from Stabilus for use on Volkswagen Passat vehicles made in 2001, 2002, 2003, 2004, and 2005. A trunk lid will not stay open by itself. Gravity will pull an unsupported lid down, hitting any body part in the way, potentially causing serious injury. A trunk strut is installed to hold up the trunk lid when needed but still allow for the lid to close. This Stabilus trunk strut will fit on Volkswagen Passats made in 2001, 2002, 2003, 2004, and 2005. It may not fit on vehicles with tailgates or hatches instead of trunks.}
